 Shell Aliases Cheatsheet
─────────────────────────────────────────────────

 LISTING (eza)
  ls              list with icons, dirs first
  l               list (long, no header)
  ll              list long + git status + header
  la              list long + hidden files + git
  lt              tree view (2 levels)
