  tree            full tree view

 DIRECTORY
  ..              cd ..
  ...             cd ../..
  ....            cd ../../..
  fcd / fj        fuzzy cd into any directory (fzf)
  z <query>       jump to frecent directory (zoxide)
  zi              interactive zoxide picker

 COMMON
  grep            grep --color=auto
